title: Rye Bread
ingredients: ['4 tablespoons chopped rye', '4 tablespoons water', '175ml milk', '4 tablespoons water', '1 teaspoon salt', '4 tablespoons dark brown soft sugar', '1 egg', '50g butter', '600g bread flour', '4 teaspoons wheat gluten powder', '1 3/4 teaspoons dried active baking yeast', '1 tablespoon milk']
